Kurulus Osman Episode 134 With Urdu Subtitles

What is going to happend in Episode 134

Yakup Bey acted before Osman Bey and conquered Lefke Castle. He says that he gave the castle to Osman Bey.Osman Bey, on the other hand, is aware that Yakup Bey is in a sneaky game. What is Yakup Bey’s intention in giving the castle to Osman Bey? Will Osman Bey accept the castle?

A new enemy comes to the Ends. This is Vasilis’s master, Master Gera. Master Gera and Osman Bey meet.But Master Gera hides his identity. He appears before Osman Bey as a merchant. Osman Bey invites him to Yenişehir. Did Osman Bey suspect Gera?

Kurulus Osman Episode 134 With Urdu Subtitles

With the arrival of Master Gera, the Ends will become even more confused. Master Gera begins his move immediately. They will kill Osman’s most trusted man in his most trusted place.

Will Vasilis be able to kill Boran?

Malhun Hatun is aware that Saadet Hatun is playing tricks with her. He will play a big trick on him. What will Malhun Hatun’s game be?To get the treasure, Orhan Bey set up a completely different game and disguised himself as a Mongol.Orhan Bey takes the treasure, but he shoots Mehmet Bey.

What will be the fate of Mehmet Bey?

Yakup Bey and Osman Bey are face to face again.Yakup Bey asks for allegiance from Osman Bey for the last time.What will Osman Bey answer?

Kurulus Osman Episode 134 With Urdu Subtitles

How will the conflict between Osman Bey and Yakup Bey end?

In the 134th episode of ‘Establishment Osman’, which was at the top of the ratings in its fifth season on ATV and attracted great attention from the audience, to be broadcast on Thursday, November 2, at 05:00 on Hadaf Play, Master Gera’s arrival in Yenişehir creates chaos, while Orhan Bey disguises himself as a Mongolian. He shoots Mehmet Bey.

Will Osman Bey take Lefke Castle from Yakup Bey?

In Episode 133 of “Kurulus Osman,” the epic Turkish historical drama series, the story continues to unfold as Osman Ghazi, the founder of the Ottoman Empire, faces numerous challenges and adversaries in his quest to establish a just and powerful state. Here’s a summary of the key events in this episode:

Internal Conflicts: Within the Kayi tribe, there are growing internal conflicts and power struggles. Some members of the tribe are hesitant to support Osman’s leadership and seek to undermine his authority. This internal tension poses a significant challenge for Osman as he endeavors to maintain order and unity.

Adversarial Forces: Osman faces increasingly ruthless adversaries both within and outside the tribe. These adversaries are determined to thwart his plans and seize power for themselves, leading to escalating tensions and confrontations.

Historical Authenticity: “Kurulus Osman” continues to excel in its historical accuracy, meticulously recreating the 13th-century setting, costumes, and architecture. This attention to detail enhances the authenticity and immersion of the series.
